blueprint.label: Chem Plant - SET EVERY BUFFER
blueprint.description:
The building not connected by wires can be deleted after the blueprint is placed!
Set the item to craft and it will craft that item of every quality until each quality meets the desired buffer amount!

entities.name: constant-combinator
entities.player_description: Buffer limits, unlocked qualities, and buffer limits as stacks

entities.name: decider-combinator
entities.player_description:
[item=buffer-chest]Status Reader
Converts buffer status to boolean states for the inserters and latches to use.
[item=red-wire]in:
-[item=parameter-0]->[item=parameter-0,quality=legendary]Buffer maximums
-[quality=normal]->[quality=legendary]Quality enable signals
[item=green-wire]in:
-[item=parameter-0]->[item=parameter-0,quality=legendary]Buffered items
Outputs:
-[[item=parameter-0]-[item=parameter-0,quality=legendary]] Buffer data
-[[quality=normal]-[quality=legendary]] Quality data

entities.name: decider-combinator
entities.player_description:
[quality=legendary]Craft Request & Latch
[item=red-wire]in: 
-[item=parameter-1,quality=legendary]->[item=parameter-6,quality=legendary]Ingredient counts
-[item=parameter-0]->[item=parameter-0,quality=legendary]Buffer status
-[quality=normal]->[quality=legendary]Quality enable signals
[item=green-wire]in:
-[virtual-signal=signal-red]reset
-[item=parameter-0]->[item=parameter-0,quality=legendary]Craft requests
Output:
-[item=parameter-0,quality=legendary]:1 - Latched request

entities.name: decider-combinator
entities.player_description:

[item=green-wire]in:
